  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
      MentalWell is a platform dedicated to supporting mental health awareness,
      self-help tools, and professional resources. We also collaborate with
      researchers to provide access to anonymized data, surveys, and
      partnerships that can help advance mental health studies.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="support">
    <h2>Support Resources</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>🧠 Self-guided exercises and journaling tools</li>
      <li>📞 Crisis hotlines and live chat support</li>
      <li>📚 Articles on anxiety, depression, and coping mechanisms</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section id="research">
    <h2>For Researchers</h2>
    <p>
      Are you conducting a study on mental health? We offer:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>🔬 Access to anonymized user data with consent</li>
      <li>📊 Survey distribution to targeted demographics</li>
      <li>🤝 Collaborative opportunities with mental health professionals</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

